    "wikipediaUrl": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latch_(song)",
    "extract": "\"Latch\" is a song by English electronic music duo Disclosure, featuring vocals from English singer Sam Smith. It was released as a digital download on 8 October 2012, by PMR Records. The lead single from their debut studio album, Settle (2013), the song debuted on the UK Singles Chart at number 26 and peaked at number 11. In the United States, \"Latch\" was a sleeper hit, peaking at number seven on the US Billboard Hot 100 in August 2014. It also reached the top 10 in Canada and France.\nIn 2022, American magazine Rolling Stone ranked \"Latch\" number 10 in their list of 200 Greatest Dance Songs of"
